{"type": "article", "id": 54380, "title": "一双能为脚部提供支撑的袜子，排汗除臭防磨损｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-06-18T23:03:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 44027, "name": "十二时慢"}, {"id": 51167, "name": "VanMoof"}, {"id": 51168, "name": "Cotto"}, {"id": 51169, "name": "Jacob Jensen Design"}, {"id": 3255, "name": "Menu"}, {"id": 51170, "name": "Helle Mardahl"}, {"id": 51171, "name": "Ib Kofod-Larsen"}, {"id": 51172, "name": "Tony Hendrix"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 203, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180618204836YOzUeXjyW0shSD4k.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Parásole - Revolutionary 3D Recovery Socks by Tony Hendrix</h3><p>我们暂且称 Parásole 为袜子，它是一种介于袜子和鞋子之间的混合体，包裹脚部时可以为脚部提供支撑和结构，缓解走路时间过长的疲劳感。</p><p>Parásole 由吸汗排汗的面料制成，360 度透气，保证双脚不出汗、无异味。袜子的底部配有一个透气柔韧的鞋底，采用 3D 打印的材料制作而成，在家中穿着的话，甚至不用穿鞋子，也能得到一定的支撑度，还有防滑功能。售价 35 美元，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/parasole-revolutionary-3d-recovery-socks-shoes-design#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618204936azoLinrHmBI9sCP7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806182049366ZXMKEVx8m9Q41Dc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806182049360s1tPy9lrCku2LX7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618204936HoP7Unbe1SjlQsI3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618204936iTY1my2QkgqtL3lP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806182049369dqpucQ6AwyjKgVB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618204936gacKhmiUSFE0487G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Knitting chair by Ib Kofod-Larsen for Menu</h3><p>丹麦设计师 Ib Kofod-Larsen 在 1950 年代设计了不少经典椅子，他偏好使用高级材料，比如玫瑰木和柚木，搭配皮革，简洁如同雕塑般的曲线，是他的设计特色。</p><p>最近，丹麦设计品牌 Menu 将 Ib Kofod-Larsen 1951 年设计的经典之作 Knitting 椅子重新量产，它有一个外露的三角形结构，微上翘的椅座，和微后倾的椅背，背部有独特的切口，预设的场景是织毛衣或者阅读时用来帮助肘部放松或者休息。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205011vdXANh9pY4SFlZqg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205012DGlspC9U8diwy5vx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205012d6rWJcG3HelgXkst.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806182050131kPBxoS6mlUIfwHE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.338832\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205013TZQ3EwGqIX9cnWO1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.425973\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/06/17/menu-reissues-knitting-chair-3-days-of-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Candy Collection by Helle Mardahl</h3><p>设计师 Helle Mardahl 最近推出了 Candy 系列灯具，灵感来源于她小时候常去的那些甜品店、糖果店，梦想能够拥有自己的一间，满是色彩、质感、欲望和孩子般的期待。Candy 系列是一组色彩绚烂的吹制玻璃灯具，Helle Mardahl 将这些橙色、蓝色、粉色和淡黄色的灯泡，想象成了一个个巨大的糖果，点亮时，它们发出柔和的光芒。</p><p>每一个灯体吹制的过程，并不追求创造完美的球体和卵形，而是允许他们有轻微的缺陷，保证每件作品都是独一无二的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205147os2xBDzl9M3XbC6t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205148fI91tgcK50slrqMm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205148yzXFZnHD2tO49YBK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205148SOr01GEdmUveiCTs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Electrified S2 and X2 by VanMoof</h3><p>Vanmoof 是目前荷兰最流行的自行车品牌之一，并在海外市场获得了很多关注。最近，他们推出了两款全新的电动自行车 Electrified S2 和Electrified X2。这两款车型都采用了极简结构，电池容量均为 504Wh，250W 齿轮前轮毂马达也能够提供不错的动力支持，续航里程可达 150Km。</p><p>为了解决车辆被盗的问题，VanMoof 使用了多项技术，包括后轮的隐形锁和防盗报警器。另外，VanMoof 还在车上加装了 GPS 定位装置，即便车辆被盗，用户也可以根据 GPS 定位找到车辆的大致位置。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=p0693ctblrh&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205237SPkVjEq8eJpfoNXy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205237x2CjDX7OqoNMPf61.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205238eOikQTSnMwCKYJyx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205238BFAI25GuDdMf9XJK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Skive collection by Jacob Jensen Design for Cotto</h3><p>泰国卫浴品牌 Cotto 推出了名为 Skive 的卫浴洁具系列，以现代北欧的设计语言为主题，操刀设计的是丹麦设计工作室 Jacob Jensen Design。Skive 系列包括洗脸盆、水龙头、马桶、花洒、淋浴间隔断等，设计团队希望通过系统化、有组织的模块设计，明确地定义卫生间的干湿区，优化日常使用习惯。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205443j7UOvazGVR6QAyeX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205444zfHNKbArRdPE2WuG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205444SeylCGXNL8vthY6k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.551184\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205444FKplPc812TQIgZDe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205444XNn5W6lIJBfgS19K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.049069\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205444OvCmDUxVsHP09MBN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205445xYXfcIuj6D5AK7ZE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.cotto.com/en/home\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cotto</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>灯侠客 by 十二时慢</h3><p>灯侠客是一款台灯，十二时慢设计团队尝试运用中国经典的侠客形象，那些头戴斗笠的侠客，给人的视觉印象深刻，他们的背影很像一盏灯。按照设计师的说法，人人都有一个侠客梦，他们只是运用了当代设计语言，重塑了关于侠客的故事。</p><p>灯侠客提供黑胡桃、大理石和亮铜三个版本，烟灰色半透玻璃灯罩+黑胡桃木灯座，低碳钢高光黑灯罩+黑色大理石等座，以及低碳钢电镀铜灯罩+低碳钢电镀铜灯座的三个组合搭配各有特色，有的犹如泼墨，有的尽显锋芒，有的柔和不刺眼。售价 1190 至 1990 元，<a href=\"http://www.12h.cn/pc/goods/show?id=18\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205658qkNUYvtDVA5xLyfR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806182056589yZlOCtBQ7V48Hxm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.552667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205658lI2mVaZgPrGMWhLU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691946\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180618205658Vw4JEyULFrholHxR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.430667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}